Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「いま！」という　この瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}なんだって　音楽に　出来たらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ　全力で　やり切ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔し涙　拭ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春のフレージング
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡が　努力の　先にあるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}限界は　あたしが決める
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一回　大げさな夢を　探しにいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}止めない　勇気こそ　強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何百回　挑戦かさねて　ここまで来た
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}チャンスの神様　みててね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}離したくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}輝きに変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いよ　届け…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「此时此刻」的这个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望能以音乐将其铭刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还未拼尽全力到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断拭去的悔恨泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是青春的分句
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若是努力之后便会有奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那极限由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}吹响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次去追寻那庞大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强大就是永不放弃的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}经历数百次的挑战　来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请机会之神看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不想忘记的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不愿放开的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}变为耀眼的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将这份心意　传递出去…！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------EDCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:25.38,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}割り切れない想いを力に変えてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:29.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無謀だと笑われた　何度も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:33.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}毎日が冒険で　青春で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:38.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい音と出会っては磨いてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:42.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}本気でやったからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:47.07,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こわい瞬間もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:47.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}届けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.96,0:22:48.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸ばしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:49.58,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:50.36,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}叶えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:55.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一度息を吹き込む　明日へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:22:59.37,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}タクトに導かれてここまで来たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:03.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたと来たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:05.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でているのは人生だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:07.80,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響くのは感情だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:12.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと忘れないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:16.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}光る音が涙を照らしてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:21.10,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}辛いことばかりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:26.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だっていつも　いつも楽しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.64,0:23:28.53,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そうでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:32.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！歌え　五線の上で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:39.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！響け　遠くの春に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:25.38,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春的苦涩变为了前进的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:29.76,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}年少冲动让我无数次被嘲笑声掩埋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:33.60,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每天都在冒险　挥洒青春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:38.35,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断磨练期待与新的乐声邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:42.40,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正因为全身心的付出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:47.07,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自然会有害怕的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:47.88,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要传递
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.96,0:22:48.78,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要触及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:49.58,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:50.36,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:55.24,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次向着奏响的明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:22:59.37,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遵循指挥棒的指引来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:03.42,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:05.88,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正在奏响的是人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:07.80,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}余音缭绕的是情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:12.84,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直都无法忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:16.64,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}耀眼的乐声将我们的泪水照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:21.10,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}并非全是辛酸经历
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:26.62,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为　一路走来有许多快乐伴随着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.64,0:23:28.53,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:32.24,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！于五线谱之上唱响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:39.29,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！向着远处胜利的春天吹响吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------------PART--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,16号参赛学校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京都府代表  北宇治高中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能像这样开展活动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都要感谢老师  各位家长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及大家的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全日本吹奏乐竞赛会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将于十月末在名古屋举行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会继续努力练习  争取在那也取得好成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请欣赏最后的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:02:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园天国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们北宇治高中吹奏乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在关西大赛上获得了金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并成功晋级了全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:34.20,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1020,720)\bord1.5\blur2\fad(500,0)}雨天的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人光顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这年头的女仆咖啡店过时了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这样可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保持微笑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3  开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  让我们做点引人注目的事吸引客人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高一三班正在开咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必光临惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这有很好吃的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家光是看  都不进来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许搞这种吸睛式女仆咖啡不是好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样能吸引到客人就是奇迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有奇迹发生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想进去喝个茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给我菜单吗  女服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了  奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很适合你  真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不适合我  说适合小绿的话还说得通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们两个还在当班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  有人感冒请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们要代班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  去哪好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我待会儿也要当班  所以得赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么去小绿推荐的猫咪咖啡店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是禁止带动物进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如去别的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有铠冢学姐的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  完全不适合服务业呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么看都是在找我茬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不记得有点过比萨斜塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是本店的特制草莓可丽饼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是附赠的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请慢慢享用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  接受这场挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人关系真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美也想吃那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了  你的好意我心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里想吃哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3\pos(962,985)}这是客人点的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的两位也关系好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}再做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:05:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:05:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有话剧演出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字叫温蒂尼妮…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还有10分钟就开演了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀一？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子学姐  全吃完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光想起来就觉得胃好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要兼顾社团又要准备学园祭很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社团那边我也会帮忙的  一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  泷老师没和你们在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才还在一起的  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是看了关西大赛后变成了他的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟之看外表是看不出性格的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和她说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:06:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您穿燕尾服超帅气…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桥本老师在那边等你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心情我懂  但说谎可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们确实是在走廊等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那哪是等着  只是在看着而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那事怎么说得出口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷老师是不是察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈刚刚又是怎样的心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以怎样的心情去对泷老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  认识的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不出是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香织学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:07:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个玩偶装是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是宣传队长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们班这次搞的是舞蹈表演
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  明日香那里你们去过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边我也很推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当有意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐那吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  要去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你们玩开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴致真高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差不多要回班级了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会当班到2点半为止  记得来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看  明日香学姐是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,welcome  迷途的小羔羊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真适合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不懂这套装扮的好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然全员都是占卜师了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会太多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  给你占卜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前的未来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是无趣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对这种应该兴致勃勃才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「好棒  那说一下我恋爱方面的事吧」像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种占卜明日香学姐能知道我的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能随便偷看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会给你占卜怎样才能使胸部变大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不劳你费心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  明日香你好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面现在很忙  你快点来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  被责备了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不可爱的学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种快点被妖怪缠住  受到诅咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼屋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是丽奈的班级…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷川？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太胆小了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:09:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别发出怪声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我的手电筒也灭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那种机关设计吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点找出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你能走慢点陪我就太谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会不会走太快了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大赛晋级真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  大家都表现得很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在下次的大赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你笑过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是久美子和冢本那吓到样子实在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是扮的妖怪太吓人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  真的是偶然碰到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冢本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱想啊  当然是偶然碰到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说台风快来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园祭没中止真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟大家准备得那么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我听说学校明天可能会放假
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你小测验还没有预习？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…因为太忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天开始又要练习了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都秋天了  却还要为了大赛练习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴随台风而来的阵风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把学园祭高涨的气氛一口气刮走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上  开始下雨的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活又完全回到了原来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范围太广了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴室洗澡水放好了  快点去洗别感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是想不念大学了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:13:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超大强力台风20号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正以时速25公里向东北方向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到明天为止请注意暴风和巨浪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量避免外出…
